data.description: Welcome home to 3218 Ruffin Green Court in the Winfield Lakes community and zoned to Fort Bend ISD!  This 2 story home features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a half bath, game room, media room, study/home office, formal living and dining rooms and a 3 car garage!! The spacious island kitchen is open to the living room and features stainless steel appliances including a double oven, granite countertops, stained cabinetry and room for bar seating.  Unwind after a long day in the super spacious 1st floor primary bedroom with sitting area. The roomy primary en-suite features a walk-in shower, dual sinks, garden tub and a spacious walk-in closet!  Don't forget to check out the community amenities like the lake with walking trial, tennis courts, playground and pool! New carpet in 1st floor formal living and dining rooms (left as you enter the front door) as well as in the front right upstairs bedroom. You don't want to miss all this great property has to offer!  Schedule your showing today!
